#fit model
m4.3 <- quap(
  alist(
    height ~dnorm(mu, sigma),
    mu <- a+b*(weight -xbar),
    a ~ dnorm(178,20),
    b ~ dlnorm(0 , 1),
    sigma ~ dunif( 0, 50)
  ),
  data = d2
)

  alist(
    height ~dnorm(mu, sigma),
    mu <- a+exp(log_b)*(weight - xbar),
    a ~ dnorm( 178, 100), 
    log_b ~ dnorm(0,1),
    sigma ~ dunif(0,50)
  ),
  data = d2
)
